@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_oltuhu(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.sin(v0)
    v1 = (0.43 - (v2 - (v1 + 0.83 * tmp + 0.97)))
    v0 = wp.exp(v0)
    v0 = ((wp.exp(v0 + 0.91) + wp.cos(v1 + 0.92)) * wp.exp(wp.cos(v1 + 0.64)))
    tmp = wp.abs(0.18)
    data[tid] = v0
